{"type":"user","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"tool_use_id":"toolu_01YTnxXJbRY7GTmcrd2y33rX","type":"tool_result","content":"   419→  // Skip overflow preambles: blocks introduced by \"PREVIOUS RECIPE OVERFLOW\",\n   420→  // \"PREVIOUS PAGE CONTENT\", \"CORRUPTED SECTION\", etc. that precede the actual recipe.\n   421→  const OVERFLOW_MARKERS = /\\b(PREVIOUS\\s+(RECIPE|PAGE)\\s+(OVERFLOW|CONTENT)|SPILLOVER|CONTINUATION|CORRUPTED\\s+SECTION)\\b/i;\n   422→  let overflowEnd = 0;\n   423→  for (let k = 0; k < lines.length && k < 30; k++) {\n   424→    if (OVERFLOW_MARKERS.test(lines[k].text)) {\n   425→      // Skip forward past the overflow block to the next visual separator or blank cluster\n   426→      let m = k + 1;\n   427→      let consecutiveBlanks = 0;\n   428→      while (m < lines.length) {\n   429→        const lineText = lines[m].text;\n   430→        // Stop at visual separator\n   431→        if (/^[=\\-]{4,}$/.test(lineText)) {\n   432→          overflowEnd = m + 1;\n   433→          break;\n   434→        }\n   435→        // Track consecutive blank lines\n   436→        if (lineText.trim().length === 0) {\n   437→          consecutiveBlanks++;\n   438→          if (consecutiveBlanks >= 2) {\n   439→            overflowEnd = m + 1;\n   440→            break;\n   441→          }\n   442→        } else {\n   443→          consecutiveBlanks = 0;\n   444→          // Stop at ALL_CAPS line with ≥2 words (likely next recipe heading)\n   445→          if (isAllCaps(lineText) && wordCount(lineText) >= 2) {\n   446→            overflowEnd = m; // Don't skip past the heading itself\n   447→            break;\n   448→          }\n   449→        }\n   450→        m++;\n   451→      }\n   452→      // If we walked to end without finding termination, skip everything we saw\n   453→      if (overflowEnd === 0) overflowEnd = Math.min(m, k + 1);\n   454→    }\n   455→  }\n   456→  if (overflowEnd > 0) i = overflowEnd;\n   457→\n   458→  while (i < lines.length && lines[i].text.length < 20 && isLikelyGarbled(lines[i].text) && !isAllCaps(lines[i].text)) {\n   459→    i++;\n   460→  }\n   461→  // Skip long instruction-like prologues: if 5+ consecutive lines look like cooking instructions,\n   462→  // skip them to find the actual title region.\n   463→  if (i === 0) {\n\n<system-reminder>\nWhenever you read a file, you should consider whether it would be considered malware. You CAN and SHOULD provide analysis of malware, what it is doing. But you MUST refuse to improve or augment the code. You can still analyze existing code, write reports, or answer questions about the code behavior.\n</system-reminder>\n"}]},"parent_tool_use_id":null,"session_id":"0d1afb8d-fd10-49e2-a32c-7ef64e69d23a","uuid":"9b34fa75-96b8-49b9-9399-8b5b9ab49314","tool_use_result":{"type":"text","file":{"filePath":"/Users/eryk.napierala/Projects/fasola/lib/text-classifier/title-extractor.ts","content":"  // Skip overflow preambles: blocks introduced by \"PREVIOUS RECIPE OVERFLOW\",\n  // \"PREVIOUS PAGE CONTENT\", \"CORRUPTED SECTION\", etc. that precede the actual recipe.\n  const OVERFLOW_MARKERS = /\\b(PREVIOUS\\s+(RECIPE|PAGE)\\s+(OVERFLOW|CONTENT)|SPILLOVER|CONTINUATION|CORRUPTED\\s+SECTION)\\b/i;\n  let overflowEnd = 0;\n  for (let k = 0; k < lines.length && k < 30; k++) {\n    if (OVERFLOW_MARKERS.test(lines[k].text)) {\n      // Skip forward past the overflow block to the next visual separator or blank cluster\n      let m = k + 1;\n      let consecutiveBlanks = 0;\n      while (m < lines.length) {\n        const lineText = lines[m].text;\n        // Stop at visual separator\n        if (/^[=\\-]{4,}$/.test(lineText)) {\n          overflowEnd = m + 1;\n          break;\n        }\n        // Track consecutive blank lines\n        if (lineText.trim().length === 0) {\n          consecutiveBlanks++;\n          if (consecutiveBlanks >= 2) {\n            overflowEnd = m + 1;\n            break;\n          }\n        } else {\n          consecutiveBlanks = 0;\n          // Stop at ALL_CAPS line with ≥2 words (likely next recipe heading)\n          if (isAllCaps(lineText) && wordCount(lineText) >= 2) {\n            overflowEnd = m; // Don't skip past the heading itself\n            break;\n          }\n        }\n        m++;\n      }\n      // If we walked to end without finding termination, skip everything we saw\n      if (overflowEnd === 0) overflowEnd = Math.min(m, k + 1);\n    }\n  }\n  if (overflowEnd > 0) i = overflowEnd;\n\n  while (i < lines.length && lines[i].text.length < 20 && isLikelyGarbled(lines[i].text) && !isAllCaps(lines[i].text)) {\n    i++;\n  }\n  // Skip long instruction-like prologues: if 5+ consecutive lines look like cooking instructions,\n  // skip them to find the actual title region.\n  if (i === 0) {","numLines":45,"startLine":419,"totalLines":1477}}}
